Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:29.33,ED-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}INSIDE　MY　FEELING　INSIDE　MY　JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:33.95,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}邪魔しないで　居場所はどこ
